creator: Techathalon
descriptionHtml:
The fastest data backup tool on Your Android Smartphone!
You will never lose your data again!

Do you fear losing your contacts ?
Always wished to backup your contacts in your mail and in your phone in this app ?
Got a latest new smart phone. Want to switch all your contacts to that phone as well ?
And here we go!!! All your questions answered in this one application.

Contacts - Backup, Scan, Restore & Delete Quickly is also called as Smart Contact Manager-Scan Contacts.

Core Functionalities:
* Contact Backup
* Scan Duplicate Contacts
* Transfer Contacts from one Phone to another one. Just in one click.

Transfer Contacts From Phone A to Phone B in one click is made possible now.

Easy Steps -
1. Download Smart Contact Manager -Scan Contacts.
2. Enter your valid details.
3 .Take Contact backup , Email it ,your backup is saved in Backup History .
4. When user gets a new cell phone he just need to Install the app Smart Contact Manager -Scan Contacts.

LOGIN WITH SAME EMAIL ID AND PASSWORD you will get all the previous backups in this app.

SCAN DUPLICATE CONTACTS
- User can Scan Duplicate Names & Numbers ,
- User can Merge or delete the Numbers in this app .


CONTACTS BACKUP
- User can view his previous backup file ,which is in VCF file .
- This file saves in app for life time if the user does not delete it.

*** DON'T WORRY if you lose your smartphones YOUR CONTACT are ALWAYS THERE ON this app for LIFETIME ***
100% SECURE , Reliable , Fast.
LIFE TIME BACKUP IN OUR APP.
Simple 4 digits PIN for your safety.
Easy backup your cell phone contacts.
Backup --> Email --> Save contacts in one Click.
View , Email , delete your Previous Backup.
Backup your contacts onto Remote Server.
Contact Backup file is ready.

Privacy Policy: https://gathademo.com/privacypolicy/?app_id=6

Enjoy..!!!
